}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#f0bc535fe6d2716d05ca5cfcdd4cf09e>.
<#f0bc535fe6d2716d05ca5cfcdd4cf09e> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
