<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2ab5c62b0120399fb0f44c1556ca82e8>.
<#2ab5c62b0120399fb0f44c1556ca82e8> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U40462>;
