<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#cecaa115415aa4237db3907853a6c11a>.
<#cecaa115415aa4237db3907853a6c11a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N03014>;
